OL,3,CMan jailed for four years for removing
OL,4,Ccondom without consent during sex
OL,6,FA man has been jailed for taking a
OL,7,Fcondom he was wearing off without
OL,8,Fconsent during sex.
OL,10,FGuy Mukendi, 39, of Brixton in south
OL,11,FLondon, was sentenced on Thursday to
OL,12,Ffour years and three months in prison,
OL,13,Fthe Metropolitan Police said.
OL,15,FMukendi was arrested following a
OL,16,Freport of sexual assault made by a
OL,17,Fyoung woman in Brixton on May 9 2023.
