OL,4,Ccondom without consent during sex
OL,6,FThe Met said the woman had consented
OL,7,Fwith Mukendi on condition that a
OL,8,Fcondom was used. But during sex, he
OL,9,Fremoved the condom without the
OL,10,Fvictim's knowledge.
OL,12,FNon-consensual condom removal is
OL,13,Fsometimes referred to as "stealthing"
OL,14,Fand is classified as rape under
OL,15,FEnglish and Welsh law.
OL,17,FThe Met said prosecutions for this
OL,18,Ftype of crime were very rare due to
OL,19,Funder-reporting.
