OL,6,FIn a press release, the force also
OL,7,Fdescribed the "milestone" case as
OL,8,F"unique".
OL,10,FLocal officers from Brixton looked at
OL,11,Ftext exchanges and forensic evidence
OL,12,Fand worked with the victim to obtain
OL,13,Fscreenshots of messages from Mukendi
OL,14,Fin which he apologised for taking the
OL,15,Fcondom off.
OL,17,FHe said he did it because he had not
OL,18,Fhad sex in a long time. He then
OL,19,Fdeleted the messages.
