OL,6,FMukendi was found guilty on April 2 at
OL,7,FInner London Crown Court, and was
OL,8,Fsentenced at the same venue on
OL,9,FThursday.
OL,11,FDetective Constable Jack Earl, who led
OL,12,Fthe investigation, said: "Throughout
OL,13,Fthis investigation, Mukendi denied any
OL,14,Fwrongdoing ` but our officers built a
OL,15,Fcompelling case against him to leave
OL,16,Fno doubt in the jury's mind.
OL,18,F"We were dedicated to securing justice
OL,19,Ffor the victim and will continue to
OL,20,Fraise awareness that this crime is a
OL,21,Fform of rape.
