OL,6,F"The victim did the right thing to
OL,7,Fcall the police straight away and her
OL,8,Fbravery should not be overshadowed.
OL,10,F"If you have been a victim of sexual
OL,11,Fviolence and not yet reported it `
OL,12,Fplease contact your local police
OL,13,Fservice and we will do all that we can
OL,14,Fto help and bring you justice."
OL,16,FKate Holmes, head of Sexual Violence
OL,17,FHelplines at Survivors Gateway, added:
OL,18,F"Survivors of sexual violence in
OL,19,FLondon can contact the Survivor's
OL,20,FGateway on 0808 801 0860 to be
OL,21,Fconnected with support.
